================================================================================
                        ATM MANAGEMENT SYSTEM LICENSE
================================================================================

Project: ATM Management System - Improved Version
Description: A comprehensive ATM management system written in C with enhanced 
            error handling, improved user interface, and better code structure.

This software includes the following components:
- Core banking operations (account management, transactions)
- User authentication system with password encryption
- Multiple account types (savings, current, fixed deposits)
- Colorful terminal user interface
- Comprehensive error handling and logging
- Input validation framework
- File-based data storage system

FEATURES COVERED BY THIS LICENSE:
✓ User Authentication (login/registration)
✓ Account Management (create, update, view, delete)
✓ Transaction Processing (deposit, withdraw)
✓ Account Transfer System
✓ Balance Inquiry Operations
✓ Interest Calculation System
✓ Error Handling Framework
✓ Input Validation System
✓ Logging and Audit Trail
✓ Terminal UI with ANSI Colors

USAGE PERMISSIONS:
- Commercial use allowed
- Modification allowed
- Distribution allowed
- Private use allowed
- Patent use allowed

LIMITATIONS:
- No warranty provided
- No liability accepted
- License and copyright notice must be included

THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS:
This software uses standard C libraries and POSIX-compliant system calls.
No external dependencies or third-party libraries are included.

BUILD REQUIREMENTS:
- GCC compiler
- Make utility
- POSIX-compliant system (Linux/macOS)

DATA HANDLING:
This software processes financial data locally. Users are responsible for:
- Securing data files (users.txt, records.txt)
- Regular backups of account information
- Compliance with local data protection regulations

SECURITY NOTICE:
This software includes basic security features:
- Password encryption using alphabetic mirroring
- Input sanitization and validation
- Access control for user accounts
- Error logging for audit trails

For production use, additional security measures may be required.

SUPPORT:
This software is provided as-is. Community support available through:
- GitHub issues and discussions
- Code documentation and comments
- Error logging system (error.log)

